---
// MCWT Scholar component with image on left and text on right
---

<section id="mcwt-scholar" class="mcwt-scholar">
	<div class="mcwt-container">
		<!-- Image Section -->
		<div class="image-section">
			<img src="/mcwt/award.jpg" alt="MCWT Scholar Award" class="mcwt-image" />
		</div>

		<!-- Text Section -->
		<div class="text-section">
			<h2 class="section-title">MCWT Scholar</h2>
			<p>
                The Michigan Council of Women in Technology (MCWT) is an organization dedicated to empowering women to pursue careers in technology and leadership roles.
            </p>
            <p>
                As an MCWT Scholar, I have been recognized for my academic achievements and work towards a successful career in technology. The scholarship has provided me with financial support, mentorship opportunities, and access to a network of professionals in the tech industry.
            </p>
            <p>
                I was further honored by being selected to speak at the MCWT Breakfast Roadshow to share my experience as a scholar.
            </p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.mcwt-scholar {
		padding: 80px 20px;
		background-color: #ffffff;
		font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
	}

	.mcwt-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 60px;
		align-items: center;
	}

	/* Image Section */
	.image-section {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.mcwt-image {
		width: 300px;
		height: auto;
		border-radius: 12px;
		background: white;
		border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
	}

	/* Text Section */
	.text-section {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: flex-start;
	}

	.text-section .section-title {
		font-size: 2.5em;
		margin: 0 0 20px 0;
		color: #1f2937;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.text-section p {
		font-size: 1.05em;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #4b5563;
		margin: 0;
	}

	/* Responsive Design */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.mcwt-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 30px;
		}

		.text-section .section-title {
			font-size: 1.8em;
		}
	}
</style>
